int iNumDocs = tempReader.numDocs();

for (int y = 0; y < iNumDocs; y++) {

Document tempDoc = tempReader.document(y);

prodWriter.addDocument(tempDoc);

}



I don't know if this is a bug in the IndexWriter.addIndexes(IndexReader)
